title: (Thurs Early) Someone Got A Major Scare from an Unknown Phone + Elder vs. Millennial with a New Twist! + Lunchbox Got Scammed!
itunes:title: (Thurs Early) Someone Got A Major Scare from an Unknown Phone + Elder vs. Millennial with a New Twist! + Lunchbox Got Scammed!
description:
Someone on the show got a major scare after getting a call from an unknown number. We try to crack the case of what really happened and who was on the other end of the call. Eddie and Abby face off in Elder vs. Millennial where the loser has to immediately eat something gross.  Lunchbox got scammed by the company and he is furious!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
